Class Spectrogram.SpectrogramResult

java.lang.Object
com.hissain.jscipy.signal.fft.Spectrogram.SpectrogramResult
Enclosing class:
Spectrogram
public static class Spectrogram.SpectrogramResult extends Object
Result holder for spectrogram computation. Contains frequencies, times, and the spectrogram matrix.

  • Field Details

    • frequencies

      public final double[] frequencies
      Array of sample frequencies.

      Length is nfft / 2 + 1 for real inputs. Units are the same as the sampling frequency fs.

    • times

      public final double[] times
      Array of segment times.

      Length corresponds to the number of time segments (frames). Units are seconds.

    • Sxx

      public final double[][] Sxx
      Spectrogram data (Power Spectral Density).

      2D array with dimensions [frequencies.length][times.length]. Sxx[i][j] corresponds to frequency frequencies[i] and time times[j].
